oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Cow/Calf Programs Using TI59 Calculator
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Hutcheson, David P.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: calculators
software
cow-calf operations
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The use of programable calculators has increased from very little usage to enthusiasm. However, software or programs have not been developed as fast as hardware. The following programs were developed to aid in fulfilling the gap of software for the TI-59. The programs are for cow-calf operations, in which information is generated for supplementation of cows on grass to feeder calf budget projections.
